name: RideOnBusSchedule
0:
”Alexa, open Ride On Bus.”
”When does the bus depart stop two five one five four?”
”When is next bus at stop two five six six zero?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ride on bus
des: This is the unofficial skill for Ride On Bus in Montgomery Country, Maryland. You can ask the skill to tell you when does the next bus depart a stop, given the five-digit stop number. You can find stop numbers on https://rideonrealtime.com/Schedule.aspx .
